These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, alhambra, prince, chaman, tiparillo, dunhill, ritmeester
1. the tiparillo-smoker is between the prince-smoker and the alhambra-smoker##2
2. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is in the middle##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is in an odd position##4
6. the prince-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
7. the aristoff-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3     |    4    |   5    |    6     |    7     |
| Cigar   | chaman | ritmeester | aristoff | dunhill | prince | tiparillo | alhambra |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, milk, 7up, iced-tea, mirinda, fanta
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2     |   3    |    4     |    5    |  6   |     7      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | cola | mirinda | soy-milk | 7up | milk | fanta |

