.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: r&b, country, disco, funk, jazz, soul, salsa
1. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
3. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
4. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
5. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
6. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
7. the fan of disco is in an even position##4
8. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |   2   |      3      |         4          |      5       |     6     |    7    |
| Music-Genre   | country | funk | r&b | jazz | salsa | disco | soul |

