2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
3. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
8. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3     |    4     |   5    |     6      |  7   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | juice | sprite | mirinda | hot-chocolate | soy-milk | milk |

