2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
8. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |  3   |   4    |   5   |  6  |  7  |
| Birthday   | september | july | october | november | january | june | april |

