.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: horror, disaster, epic, spy, zombie, documentary, drama
 1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 4. the person watching zombie movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 6. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
 8. the person watching documentary movies is in an odd position##4
 9. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
10. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |  2   |  3   |  4   |     5      |     6     |  7   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | horror | drama | spy | zombie | epic | documentary |

 